{"type": "article", "id": 28655, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 29369, "name": "Roland"}, {"id": 22528, "name": "karimoku"}, {"id": 16335, "name": "Plumen"}, {"id": 29370, "name": "KALO"}, {"id": 25700, "name": "Roche Bobois"}, {"id": 29371, "name": "B&B studio"}, {"id": 29372, "name": "Stephen Burks"}, {"id": 29373, "name": "Akshay Patil"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163704wcO0JUj8kzebVguE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p>\n<h2>Kiyola KF-10 by Karimoku</h2>\n<p>电子乐器制造商罗兰（<a href=\"http://www.roland.com/\">Roland</a>）与日本家具设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.karimoku-newstandard.jp/\">Karimoku</a> 联手推出纯手工制作的木制电钢琴 Kiyola KF-10，是一款将数码乐器与家居结合在一起的产品。它的饰面采用的是核桃木和纯橡木这样的低甲醛木材，不仅环保，也带来了赏心悦目的木质肌理花纹。Karimoku 还设计了一把符合人体工程学的钢琴凳：呈拱形的高密度坐垫能够更均匀地分布重量，减少久坐对身体造成的损伤。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164731nyxZleEJNkM4VDTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164732V5ERquBHyZvkXdNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45843521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164732IkEuxOG9dtZyDqMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164733ZWf3SwaQ75PsO6RM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647331O6dn0EMmSRp3DcW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164734984cJv0dKtqAawRo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Memoir collection by Plumen</h2>\n<p>设计工作室 <a href=\"http://plumen.com/\">Plumen</a> 最近与 <a href=\"Made.comhttp://www.made.com/\">Made.com</a> 再次合作，从 1950 年代的工作灯中汲取灵感，推出了 Memoir 系列灯具。这一系列包括了吊灯、台灯以及壁灯，配备的是 Plumen 002 LED 灯泡以及金属的网纱灯罩，昏黄的灯光从空隙中扩散开来，营造出朦胧的氛围。黑金金属与黄铜的搭配看上去非常典雅，有着浓浓的复古感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216473484J90GCmoziVaE3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164734inZ7HrFPXVQp5qaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164735dXSEjFi82tcRerIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164735UGV7F3JXialcOskP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164736bAKUsnkeSNj4cMwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164736BWzXAOegpCTxfKU8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Multi-Tier Shelf by KALO</h2>\n<p>如果你不喜欢在木制家具上看到太多用来固定的五金件，工作室 <a href=\"http://www.ammarkalo.com/\">KALO</a> 近日设计的木架 Multi-Tier Shelf 或许会让你眼前一亮。这款木架最大的特点在于它的一体化设计，四根木腿依靠顶部的黄铜钉可以轻松地进行折叠或者调整高度，省去了不少运输和组装时的麻烦。在穿过下面的搁板时，缺口处的皮革衬垫则会护住木腿防止它们往下滑落。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.ammarkalo.com/Multi-Tier-Shelf\">链接</a>了解木架的详细规格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164737rkxTEOYKS8QiWjR4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164737bqDSrsx91B7Hd3Xv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164738WaqCYmfkSNPHcysj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164738EFk46G5asfIiVMHQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164739vxSfoMGwkT98KVF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Traveler by Stephen Burks</h2>\n<p>设计师 <a href=\"http://www.stephenburksmanmade.com/\">Stephen Burks</a> 曾在 2015 年为 <a href=\"http://www.roche-bobois.com/en-US\">Roche Bobois</a> 四十周年设计了一套名为 Traveler 的户外家具，其中包括了两款色彩鲜艳的扶手椅。在系列的新品中，Burks 把管状的喷漆钢结构同五颜六色的灯芯绒靠垫结合在了一起，并且以印尼手工艺为灵感设计了两套不同的配色，为这个系列注入了一股亚洲风情。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164739ig5W0ZB4tX9EopLx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164740SL2x4sIpZ8nvF3BV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164741eQz75BqWPVJMoTbh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164741IuWNcTrVJkf0nEh8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164741EkFTMfzaOyN9VPd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164742LnfYMcGVAgUXoNeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>LumeWheel by Akshay Patil</h2>\n<p>这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/38678055/LumeWheel-Minimalist-Clock\">LumeWheel</a> 的挂钟是印度设计师 Akshay Patil 的作品，参考了船的舵盘进行设计。Patil 省去了钟面，仅留下一个镂空的金属圆环，LED 灯的位置表示刻度，一大一小两个指针分别代表了分和秒，时针则由点亮的 LED 灯替代。LumeWheel 还会根据时间切换灯光颜色（午前蓝色，午后黄色），看上去科技感十足。挂钟目前还处于原型阶段，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164742wslJ5EFu86TtnvRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55773196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164743v9X7H8RGIs0KWLA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164743teJXqT2dMRUNA4fs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164743sELqpxFSV8KNhcfw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Dalston’s soft drinks by B&amp;B studio</h2>\n<p>Dalston 是英国伦敦的一家汽水公司，近日委托了 <a href=\"http://www.bandb-studio.co.uk/\">B&amp;B studio</a> 设计一套强调品牌主张的包装。设计师们在包装上保留了“伦敦制造”以及“手工捣碎”这两句标语，并且巧妙地将捣碎动作组成品牌的首字母 D 与不同的原料对应，既直观又很有趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164744zaRVDZ5pLM7u3WoQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74933333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647457v3BD9Sxc01RHahs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647452wy78CiL0O1qzrpa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.84\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}